reviewText: Came right on time and in great condition. Cute kids series. My kids love it.
My son loves this series and it made a perfect gift!
Really love this show. It's pretty good but its kind of a guilty pleasure of mine. All the same though its worth checking out.

So, on the packaging, it claims to be the complete third season, but it lacks the series/season 3 finale, An All Dogs Christmas Carol, unlike the complete series set. I think it's still well worth it though as it is a great show. And if you are to save money, seasons 1-3 and An All Dogs Christmas Carol may be your best bet.
Can't go wrong with the series sets! Great memories will abound while watching and the clearness of the graphics makes a lot of difference from years ago.
